fr.xephi.authme.process.register.executors

Class RegistrationMethod<P extends RegistrationParameters>

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.xephi.authme.process.register.executors.RegistrationMethod<P>
  • Type Parameters:
    P - the registration parameters type the method uses

    public final class RegistrationMethod<P extends RegistrationParameters>
extends Object
    Methods with which a player can be registered.

    These constants each define a different way of registering a player and define the parameters and executor classes which perform this registration method. This is essentially a typed enum as passing a constant of this class along with a parameters object to a method can be restricted to the correct parameters type.
